comment:
* The template class is used to call callback functions on events from the TBS server. Callback
     * functions are wrapped in this class and registered to the Android system during app
     * registration.
     *
     * @hide

methods.name: public abstract void onAcceptCall(int requestId, @NonNull UUID callId)
methods.comment:
* Called when a remote client requested to accept the call. * *

An application must call {@link BluetoothLeCallControl#requestResult} to complete the * request. * * @param requestId The Id of the request * @param callId The call Id requested to be accepted * @hide

methods.name: public abstract void onTerminateCall(int requestId, @NonNull UUID callId)
methods.comment:
* A remote client has requested to terminate the call. * *

An application must call {@link BluetoothLeCallControl#requestResult} to complete the * request. * * @param requestId The Id of the request * @param callId The call Id requested to terminate * @hide

methods.name: public void onHoldCall(int requestId, @NonNull UUID callId)
methods.comment:

An application must call {@link BluetoothLeCallControl#requestResult} to complete the * request. * * @param requestId The Id of the request * @param callId The call Id requested to be put on hold * @hide

methods.name: public void onUnholdCall(int requestId, @NonNull UUID callId)

methods.name: public abstract void onPlaceCall(int requestId, @NonNull UUID callId, @NonNull String uri)
